Package: MetaboDiff
Type: Package
Title: An R package for differential metabolomic analysis
Version: 0.9.5
Author: Andreas Mock
Maintainer: <andreas.mock@nct-heidelberg.de>
Description: The MetaboDiff packages aims to provide a low-level entry to differential metabolomic analysis by starting off with the table of relative metabolite quantifications provided by commercial vendors or core facilities. 
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.2),
    SummarizedExperiment,
    MultiAssayExperiment,
    ComplexHeatmap,
    tidyverse
Imports:
    impute,
    vsn,
    cowplot,
    WGCNA,
    ape,
    dynamicTreeCut,
    plyr,
    phytools,
    tsne,
    genefilter
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests: BiocStyle, knitr, rmarkdown
